罪活動(aiding and abetting criminal activities)」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，現任《南華早報》總編輯譚衛兒(Tammy Tam)在廣東湛江出生長大，於廣州中山大學畢業，譚衛兒與中聯辦人士「情同姊妹」，曾在二零零七至二零一一年間在亞洲電視任新聞總監，在王維基短暫主導亞視期間，由於王維基希望亞視擺脫「中央台」形象，曾嘗試除去譚衛兒而不果。<br />\n<br />\n直至目前，特區警察已在「反送中條例運動」拘捕逾百名人士，這些人士將被起訴非法集結、非法集會、暴動、藏有攻擊性武器、襲警、襲擊致造成身體傷害、普通襲擊、在公眾地方打架、有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦、披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料、刑事毀壞、威脅會摧毀或損壞財產或刑事恐嚇等罪。//<br />\n<br />\n協助與教唆犯罪活動？？？咩料呀？<br />\n馬雲SCMP嚇鬼？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"真心驚"},{"pid":"f217cb2357b5eed5a2f67bf9ef6bb2e8830c9faf","tid":1336554,"uid":169865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucdCWmi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucdCWmi.gif&h=bc2736e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c860681c1360825782a4f69ca942b4f0da7cbcf","tid":1336554,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a64f9e77ddda65696acf8a8637a646e2fdbc037","tid":1336554,"uid":176166,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6200411a2db307ea65689824556e16f4f073efd5","tid":1336554,"uid":73192,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"b70ef0687351843e38950617895aa730604675dd","tid":1336554,"uid":50457,"like":244,"dislike":1,"score":243,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"唔覺得法庭會認可呢個方法 除非有明顯特徵<br />\n好難証明真係佢黎 疑點利益歸被告<br />\n利伸唔識法律"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18f58ec9da3a9588bc758d47ed9de7632b1d3f6","tid":1336554,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"警察現正利用人臉辨識科技認人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /